description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Core Strength' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Groove Session and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The The Groove Session vibe means Fun, fluid, expressive, completely in the moment. This is especially good for Days when you want to move intuitively and just vibe. The The Endorphin Wave vibe means Elevated energy, feel-good movement, steady build. This is especially good for When you want a challenging but steady burn..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Ignite your core with Peter and Dani from the helicopter pad at the Four Seasons in Los Angeles. ...
